limited. All funktions are full available.

Step 1:

Use TXADRREGISTRATOR and follow carefully and exactly the instructions.
It is very important to keep the Subject ADREG. Also do not make any changes
to the generated mail, because the mailparser and the serializer would get
wrong informations to complete their operations successfully.

Step 2:

Submit the mail, generated by the Registrator to saxon@wizard.art-line.de
with the subject ADREG .

Step 3:

Routing dependent a confirmation will reach You after 1-6 days.
The UU encoded keyfile will follow. This personal key has to be decoded and
moved to the PROGDIR: of the program.


